metadata.name: TwentyPuzzles #1/20
metadata.description: Twenty Puzzles will drop in batches of Twenty.  When they are sold it is the buyers responsibility to reach out to us so we can get them the puzzle.  We will put your NFT or Your projects NFT/LOGO or IRL Business logo, family photo, WHATEVER you get the point! We will put any picture on a puzzle, and then turn that puzzle into an NFT collectible for you to have on the blockchain as well.
